incidents.name: SMS Delivery Failures from Denmark Mobile Networks to a Subset of Twilio's Denmark Long Codes

incident_updates.body: We continue experiencing SMS delivery failures from Denmark mobile networks to a subset of Twilio's Denmark long codes. Our engineers are working with our carrier partner to resolve the issue. We expect to provide another update in 4 hours or as soon as more information becomes available.

We are still experiencing SMS delivery failures from Denmark mobile networks to a subset of Twilio's Denmark long codes. Our engineers are working with our carrier partner to resolve the issue. We expect to provide another update in 2 hours or as soon as more information becomes available.

We are experiencing SMS delivery failures from Denmark Mobile Networks to a subset of Twilio's Denmark long codes. Our engineers are working with our carrier partner to resolve the issue. We expect to provide another update in 1 hour or as soon as more information becomes available.

incidents.name: Low Volume of 500s Returned Instead of 400s for MMS Messages

incident_updates.body: We have identified a solution for providing appropriate Twilio error code and http status codes when customers send MMS messages. We expect to provide another update in 8 hours or as soon as more information becomes available.

We have identified a solution for providing appropriate Twilio error code and http status codes when customers send MMS messages. We expect to provide another update in another 1 hour or as soon as more information becomes available.

We continue to investigate the issue with MMS low volume of 500s being returned instead of 400s resulting in unnecessary retries from the customer. We expect to provide another update in 4 hours or as soon as more information becomes available.
